    <item>
      <title>泰森食品计划在火灾后分阶段重启佐治亚州肉类加工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/tyson-plans-to-restart-georgia-meat-plant-in-phases-after-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，泰森食品公司计划分阶段重启佐治亚州一家肉类加工厂。该加工厂上周发生火灾，造成一人死亡，数人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/tyson-plans-to-restart-georgia-meat-plant-in-phases-after-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 18:42:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
